@NODE Introduction
@{B}Introduction@{UB}

WinRes can extract files from Windows resource files such as .EXE, .DLL,
.ICL, etc.  Currently it can only extract .ICO files from Windows 3.1
files but in the future I plan to support more formats (if I can get
information about them).

WinRes can be used with CUR2ILBM (also written by me) to convert .ICO,
.CUR, .ANI files into IFF-ILBM files so that they can be viewed/edited
easily with other utilities for the Amiga.

@ENDNODE

